{"tid":293864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】究竟啲廢老識唔識去廁所","createTime":"2017-06-22T13:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T20:14:47.000Z","uid":54023,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dcd92703e90a1d7df28d63f9b858dea81a05513","tid":293864,"uid":54023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s6qf97ed\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs6qf97ed&h=c685f52c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行埋去見到啲屎真係想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢事嚇到大家<br />\n所以冇影<br />\n同埋有5格4格都係咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc809914cf553812010a8123be69f4508212487","tid":293864,"uid":70706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"最誇張見過有人柯喺廁板上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fa4c58cce14d6df3074d5e242be56356e0622f","tid":293864,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"你又知係廢老？"},{"pid":"c478ce19b30ce1619dccb60d110d4eae8c8a8b70","tid":293864,"uid":54023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又知係廢老？</blockquote><br />\n雖然係標籤左，但直覺黎，因為成日撞到啲阿伯行出黎個廁所就好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b131bc43e9b05c2009ec098ed64c86191c7a99","tid":293864,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"做哩啲廁所既清潔工真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7027ab952581c261f65f670b41f23b183fa44208","tid":293864,"uid":84918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"佢地失禁"},{"pid":"17dce2e9cc725c4030bb3140083e228c8ed60df0","tid":293864,"uid":62079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最誇張見過有人柯喺廁板上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見過牆上面都有，仲要eye level咁高，你唔會想像到點樣噴上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e5935109a326c0f901e0519e811714a46b652d","tid":293864,"uid":43308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1719c2a3146a3f515a1557e7a1aca85833816a04","tid":293864,"uid":54023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔關識唔識去廁所/衛生意識問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲窮廢中、窮廢老成世人冇乜成就 冇社會地位 感受不到尊重 長期覺得被漠視/鄙視/輕視<br />\n<br />\n覺得社會永遠 ill-treat 佢哋, 出現反社會人格, 心理上需要報復社會, 刻意挑戰公德, 因為佢哋認為[遵守公德]得不到正面回應 (&quot;做好人冇好報&quot;, &quot;我咁有德行都賭輸馬炒燶股? 咁品德有閪用?&quot;), 總括而言, 係長期精神壓迫嘅反撲: &quot;我畀商家佬壓榨咗成世, 整污穢你班商家佬嘅廁所少少都唔柒得?&quot; / &quot;我顧人感受, 邊個顧我感受? 哂尻氣&quot;. 刻意嘅反社會行為模式(consciously antisocial behavior).<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係心理問題, 唔係衛生意識問題。 成長背景之中缺乏互信精神、公民契約精神嘅人群全部都有咁嘅心理現象: 中國大陸廢中廢老、香港廢中廢老、印度窮人、etc.. 　佢地唔係唔覺得/唔意識到污穢, 只係覺得「非我之責」。呢班人嘅扭曲心理嘅共通點: 「個世界係咁架啦, 咁你想點?」/「係弱肉強食架喎, 講良心? 你傻撚咗啊?」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 業餘心理學家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">利申9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6efe8a555d8c1b3ce700a3bf76daa1a80638786","tid":293864,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"<bloc